### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَلَا تَمْشِ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ مَرَحًا ۖ إِنَّكَ لَن تَخْرِقَ ٱلْأَرْضَ وَلَن تَبْلُغَ ٱلْجِبَالَ طُولًا</span>

### English

And do not walk on the earth arrogantly. Surely you can neither crack the earth nor stretch to the height of the mountains.